<p id="P1"><strong>Contributorship statement</strong></p>
<p id="P2">All authors were involved in drafting the article or revising it critically for important intellectual content, and all authors approved the final version to be published. Dr. Javaid had full access to all of the data in the study and takes responsibility for the integrity of the data and the accuracy of the data analysis.</p>
<p id="P3">-Study conception and design: Lyles, Prieto-Alhambra, Arden, Judge, Cooper, and Javaid.</p>
