<th align="left" valign="top" rowspan="1" colspan="1">Impaired cognitive<br>function (SPMSQ &gt;2)</th>
<th align="left" valign="top" rowspan="1" colspan="1"></th>
</tr></thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td align="center" valign="top" rowspan="1" colspan="1"></td>
<td align="left" valign="top" rowspan="1" colspan="1">N = 1,616</td>
