<td align="center" valign="top" rowspan="1" colspan="1">Chi-<br>square<br>p-value</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="center" valign="top" rowspan="1" colspan="1">
<strong>Clinical</strong>
<br>
<strong>fracture</strong>
